# backend/.env.example
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this to backend/.env and fill in a real value — backend/.env is
# gitignored, so it never leaves your machine. For production (Render),
# set the same variable in the dashboard instead: Service → Environment.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# AI Assistant — free-tier Groq API key (Llama 3.3 70B).
# Get one at console.groq.com → API Keys → Create API Key.
# The chat endpoint degrades gracefully with this unset — /chat will
# just return an error message instead of crashing the whole server.
GROQ_API_KEY=
